Package: VecchiaCensored
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Modeling for Censored Data Using Vecchia Approximations
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-27
Authors@R: person("Yacine", "IDIR", 
                  email = "yacine-epst@hotmail.com")
Description: Efficient spatial modeling for censored and uncensored observations
    using Vecchia approximations. Supports simple Gaussian processes (GP) and 
    spatially varying coefficients (SVC) with both Bayesian (Stan) and frequentist 
    inference. Handles left-censored data common in environmental monitoring.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
